<h2>ASCII Gnu</h2>

<pre>
  ,           , 
 /             \ 
((__-^^-,-^^-__)) 
 `-_---' `---_-' 
  `--|o` 'o|--' 
     \  `  / 
      ): :( 
      :o_o: 
       "-" 
</pre>

<p>
This is an ASCII drawing of a gnu's head, suitable for non-graphical
terminals.
</p>
